What you need to know:

The Kipchoge Keino Stadium situated in Eldoret, Uasin Gishu County, is expected to host Olympics Games trials ahead of the July 23 to August 8 Tokyo Games. The trials normally act as a “mini-Olympics” with those selected to join the team most probably bagging medals. In 2016, the Eldoret stadium hosted the trials for the team for the Rio Olympics Games, attracting a massive crowd. 